				<h5>Hobgoblins/Goblinas:</h5>
				<p>Male goblins undergo evolution into Hobgoblins, while their female counterparts transform into Goblinas. These evolved forms demonstrate heightened intelligence, improved health, and increased muscularity compared to their goblin predecessors.</p>
				
