				<h5>Kijin:</h5>
				<p>Kijin, being the evolutions of Ogres, represent a high-class monster race with exceptional abilities. Each Kijin possesses remarkable potential in various fields, surpassing humans in artistry, whether in magic, swordsmanship, ninja skills, elemental mastery, and more. Renowned for their formidable power, Kijin are invaluable allies in warfare, with their abundance of magicules surpassing their Ogre predecessors.</p>

