				<h4>Orc family:</h4>
				
				<h5>Orcs:</h5>
				<p>Orcs stand markedly weaker than Ogres, relying on their strength in numbers for compensation. Resembling pigs in appearance, Orcs are less intelligent, even among monsters, which is compensated by their substantial muscular power. </p>
				
				<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
