				<h5>Dryads:</h5>
				<p>Dryads, specialised spirits and embodiments of nature serve as the dedicated caretakers of the Great Forest of Jura. Typically concealing themselves, they possess comprehensive knowledge of all events within the forest. In their role as guardians, Dryads administer divine judgment to those who pose harm to the forest.</p>
				
